"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Indicator states","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indeterminate"}]},{"text":": like a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In you are looking for a checkbox with only two possible values, refer to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Particular cases","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for checkbox.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Cases forbidden by design","level":2,"anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Code samples","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple checkbox, but is an error context","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate(selection: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\"), isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Suggestions","level":2,"anchor":"Suggestions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"According to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"reference","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}],"isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange","level":3,"anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Orange Business Tools","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Sosh","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Wireframe","level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkbox_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Version","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent